text: Old Street shops surrounded area linked to hazi lane with small pubs n gift shop around n very close to bus stoppage.

There are 3 bus routes passing through this station: 2N, 4N, 48. The focus is on the two alleys behind the station. It is the most fashionable, colorful and eye-catching attraction in my country. During the day, a large number of tourists come to sightsee and take photos; at night It is a dining place with a romantic atmosphere. Haji lane (Haji lane), Bali lane (Bali lane) - one by one is now "red"!
